Pull over. I want you to stop the car.

578
00:28:20,933 --> 00:28:22,088
Unlock the door.

579
00:28:26,530 --> 00:28:27,400
Unlock it!

580
00:28:33,690 --> 00:28:34,080
Shuishan,

581
00:28:34,730 --> 00:28:35,290
wait!

582
00:28:35,866 --> 00:28:37,244
I shouldn't have said that!

583
00:28:43,320 --> 00:28:43,690
Dad,

584
00:28:44,360 --> 00:28:46,490
who was that scruffy-looking guy
just now?

585
00:28:46,700 --> 00:28:48,490
He looked like someone
with serious training.

586
00:28:49,690 --> 00:28:51,090
That was Le Shuishan's ex-boyfriend.

587
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:54,320
Come on, don't overdo it just for love.

588
00:28:58,210 --> 00:28:59,690
Even if I tried, I couldn't beat him.

589
00:29:00,360 --> 00:29:01,450
The guy used to do kayaking.

590
00:29:02,290 --> 00:29:03,160
So what if he's tough?

591
00:29:03,690 --> 00:29:04,490
He's retired now.

592
00:29:05,600 --> 00:29:06,210
Besides, Dad,

593
00:29:07,644 --> 00:29:08,600
relationships aren't

594
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:11,250
about physical strength, right?

595
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:14,210
It's about being in sync, soul to soul.

596
00:29:14,530 --> 00:29:15,730
Having the same wavelength.

597
00:29:16,730 --> 00:29:17,160
Yes.

598
00:29:18,080 --> 00:29:19,250
He's an ex for a reason.

599
00:29:19,777 --> 00:29:21,320
Clearly, they drifted apart over time,

600
00:29:21,530 --> 00:29:23,080
because they were no longer aligned.

601
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:26,210
Done.

602
00:29:28,250 --> 00:29:28,560
Okay.

603
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:38,120
Hi, Shuishan!

604
00:29:39,600 --> 00:29:40,400
Do you like it?

605
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:42,290
I love it!

606
00:29:43,050 --> 00:29:43,880
It's beautiful!

607
00:29:44,120 --> 00:29:45,730
The ladies in the choir said

608
00:29:45,730 --> 00:29:48,360
you got hurt because you
were taking pictures for us,

609
00:29:48,360 --> 00:29:49,866
so we should take responsibility.

610
00:29:49,933 --> 00:29:53,490
So, they sent me to look after you.

611
00:29:53,690 --> 00:29:56,080
Oh, so you're here
on behalf of everyone?

612
00:29:56,577 --> 00:29:58,844
And here I thought you came
because you wanted to.

613
00:29:58,866 --> 00:30:00,600
I came because I wanted to, of course.

614
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:02,880
Now that makes me happy!

615
00:30:02,888 --> 00:30:03,400
Come on.

616
00:30:03,577 --> 00:30:04,210
Have a seat.

617
00:30:04,290 --> 00:30:05,533
Is your leg feeling any better?

618
00:30:05,800 --> 00:30:07,530
Much better than yesterday.

619
00:30:08,244 --> 00:30:09,560
Still, don't push it too fast.

620
00:30:09,730 --> 00:30:11,010
Got it. Come on, sit here.

621
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:24,400
Yesterday,

622
00:30:25,050 --> 00:30:27,120
when Heibao left, I forgot to thank him.

623
00:30:28,080 --> 00:30:29,450
Li Heibao

624
00:30:30,010 --> 00:30:31,250
is really built,

625
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:33,120
and super helpful,

626
00:30:34,360 --> 00:30:35,730
just not much of a talker.

627
00:30:36,022 --> 00:30:38,644
I tried making conversation on the way,
but he didn't say a word.

628
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,250
That's just how he is.

629
00:30:41,530 --> 00:30:44,010
Yesterday should've been
something really touching.

630
00:30:44,010 --> 00:30:45,530
I really was grateful to him.

631
00:30:45,530 --> 00:30:45,970
But then

632
00:30:46,730 --> 00:30:48,530
he said something that really upset me.

633
00:30:49,711 --> 00:30:50,490
What did he say?

634
00:30:52,290 --> 00:30:53,640
He said that I'm just a replacement

635
00:30:54,290 --> 00:30:55,250
to your family.

636
00:31:01,930 --> 00:31:02,880
Oh, Heibao...

637
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:05,530
Am I?

638
00:31:09,530 --> 00:31:10,080
Shuishan,

639
00:31:11,930 --> 00:31:13,530
you do look a lot like Jingmin.

640
00:31:14,490 --> 00:31:15,120
So at first,

641
00:31:16,250 --> 00:31:17,600
the kids and I

642
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:20,120
naturally felt a closeness to you.

643
00:31:21,044 --> 00:31:22,066
But over time,

644
00:31:22,066 --> 00:31:23,160
as we got to know you,

645
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:24,266
we came to understand,

646
00:31:25,450 --> 00:31:26,160
that you're you.

647
00:31:27,044 --> 00:31:27,977
You're not her.

648
00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:34,880
So, I'm not a replacement

649
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:36,970
to you?

650
00:31:38,730 --> 00:31:39,360
Of course not.

651
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:43,450
I should pour you a cup of tea.

652
00:31:43,450 --> 00:31:44,640
Don't get up.

653
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:45,600
Let me make tea for you.

654
00:31:46,533 --> 00:31:48,511
You ended up having to make it yourself.

655
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:00,360
Take a look.

656
00:32:00,770 --> 00:32:02,160
Is this Smiling Tiger?

657
00:32:02,244 --> 00:32:03,120
I just ran into him.

658
00:32:06,555 --> 00:32:07,360
Everything okay?

659
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,490
I... I have to go.

660
00:32:11,155 --> 00:32:12,244
I'll be right back.

661
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:16,160
Try to stay calm!

662
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:27,120
Le Shuishan!

663
00:32:27,690 --> 00:32:28,640
What do you want?

664
00:32:28,770 --> 00:32:29,530
Smiling Tiger,

665
00:32:29,733 --> 00:32:31,770
my husband beat you up
because you harassed me.

666
00:32:32,044 --> 00:32:34,733
You got back at him by transferring
him to the Gobi Desert.

667
00:32:35,450 --> 00:32:36,880
Now he's dead.

668
00:32:37,560 --> 00:32:39,160
They can't even find his body.

669
00:32:39,530 --> 00:32:40,360
Le Shuishan,

670
00:32:40,930 --> 00:32:42,970
Zhang Yali was transferred

671
00:32:43,080 --> 00:32:44,930
because we received a formal complaint.

672
00:32:45,120 --> 00:32:46,880
He was accused of harassing our doctor

673
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:48,360
