678
00:32:57,600 --> 00:32:58,290
Slander?

679
00:32:58,450 --> 00:32:59,840
Now you know what that word means?

680
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:01,640
When you accused me of harassment,

681
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,930
why didn't you call that slander?

682
00:33:03,050 --> 00:33:05,050
You're disgusting!

683
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:07,290
