688
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:13,120
Shuishan!

689
00:33:13,450 --> 00:33:13,970
Calm down!

690
00:33:14,111 --> 00:33:14,640
Calm down!

691
00:33:16,088 --> 00:33:17,000
You're bleeding!

692
00:33:17,120 --> 00:33:17,600
It's blood.

693
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:18,770
Calm down!

694
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,640
I'm sorry, Yali.

695
00:33:49,730 --> 00:33:50,840
Our child

696
00:33:55,050 --> 00:33:56,250
