with one coach each.

700
00:34:32,490 --> 00:34:33,760
These are all our leaders.

701
00:34:34,200 --> 00:34:35,760
Please give them the best service, okay?

702
00:34:36,450 --> 00:34:37,810
Most importantly, stay safe.

703
00:34:38,530 --> 00:34:39,530
Safety comes first.

704
00:34:39,720 --> 00:34:41,244
Nothing is more important than that.

705
00:34:42,050 --> 00:34:42,810
Which one is mine?

706
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:43,822
This one.

707
00:34:45,160 --> 00:34:46,370
Please keep it stable for me.

708
00:34:47,080 --> 00:34:47,760
I'm

709
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:49,530
