712
00:34:59,244 --> 00:35:01,155
Your paddle hit mine.

713
00:35:05,720 --> 00:35:07,240
Stop!

714
00:35:07,370 --> 00:35:09,244
What? You can't even
keep your paddles apart.

715
00:35:09,266 --> 00:35:10,680
What kind of coach are you?

716
00:35:11,066 --> 00:35:12,240
I'm filing a complaint.

717
00:35:12,850 --> 00:35:13,560
What's your name?

718
00:35:14,555 --> 00:35:15,160
Take a guess.

719
00:35:20,933 --> 00:35:21,810
Don't want to guess?

720
00:35:22,866 --> 00:35:23,810
I'll guess for you.

721
00:35:24,810 --> 00:35:26,640
Your name is Tang Jialin, right?

722
00:35:29,050 --> 00:35:30,410
They call you Smiling Tiger.

723
00:35:30,577 --> 00:35:31,450
That's you, isn't it?

724
00:35:31,930 --> 00:35:32,760
There was a woman

725
00:35:33,490 --> 00:35:34,760
at your company, Le Shuishan.

726
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:35,690
You know her, don't you?

727
00:35:36,930 --> 00:35:37,490
Who are you?

728
00:35:37,560 --> 00:35:39,088
Her husband, Zhang Yali. Remember him?

729
00:35:40,200 --> 00:35:42,930
The Zhang Yali who died
in some godforsaken place?

730
00:35:44,911 --> 00:35:46,311
What do you want?

731
00:35:53,080 --> 00:35:53,890
What do I want?

732
00:35:55,810 --> 00:35:56,890
The first hit

733
00:35:58,533 --> 00:35:59,410
is for Zhang Yali.

734
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:02,450
A kind, decent young man

735
00:36:03,530 --> 00:36:05,490
died because of your personal vendetta.

736
00:36:07,640 --> 00:36:08,640
You hit me!

737
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:10,720
The second hit

738
00:36:11,160 --> 00:36:12,010
is for Le Shuishan.

739
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,890
Widowed so young,

740
00:36:14,600 --> 00:36:15,530
left all alone,

741
00:36:15,911 --> 00:36:17,410
and endured years of hardship.

742
00:36:19,120 --> 00:36:20,640
Sir! Sir!

743
00:36:21,066 --> 00:36:23,080
There's been a misunderstanding!

744
00:36:23,370 --> 00:36:24,410
Stop talking nonsense.

745
00:36:25,050 --> 00:36:27,450
I've stared at your face in
photos for three whole years.

746
00:36:28,377 --> 00:36:30,280
I could recognize you
from a pile of dust.

747
00:36:30,930 --> 00:36:31,850
And the third hit

748
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,160
is for their child

749
00:36:33,930 --> 00:36:34,890
who died

750
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:38,720
before even getting to see this world.

751
00:36:48,530 --> 00:36:50,410
I can't swim!

752
00:36:51,490 --> 00:36:52,080
Heibao!

753
00:36:52,890 --> 00:36:53,810
Heibao!

754
00:36:58,370 --> 00:36:59,200
Help me, sir!

755
00:36:59,370 --> 00:36:59,850
Sir,

756
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:01,850
I can't...

757
00:37:02,490 --> 00:37:03,720
I can't swim!

758
00:37:10,330 --> 00:37:10,760
Sir!

759
00:37:11,370 --> 00:37:13,200
I can't swim, sir!

760
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:23,490
Heibao!

761
00:37:54,450 --> 00:37:54,930
Coming.

762
00:38:05,240 --> 00:38:05,760
Shuishan.

763
00:38:06,050 --> 00:38:06,760
Mr. Shen?

764
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:09,720
You left in such a hurry today.

765
00:38:10,240 --> 00:38:11,120
I was worried.

766
00:38:11,120 --> 00:38:12,244
So I came to check on you.

767
00:38:12,370 --> 00:38:12,970
I'm sorry.

768
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:15,050
I left without saying goodbye.

769
00:38:17,155 --> 00:38:17,930
Have a seat.

770
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:18,600
Okay.

771
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:21,530
Oppo!

772
00:38:23,330 --> 00:38:24,410
It's been a while.

773
00:38:28,930 --> 00:38:30,680
Do you remember what I told you before?

774
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:32,410
About the man who got my husband killed?

775
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:35,044
The one they call Smiling Tiger?

776
00:38:35,810 --> 00:38:37,010
I remember. What about him?

777
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:38,850
Would you believe it,

778
00:38:39,488 --> 00:38:40,930
turns out he was leading a team

779
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:44,810
