780
00:38:44,970 --> 00:38:46,970
And wouldn't you know it,
he ran into Heibao.

781
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:51,370
Talk about walking right into it.

782
00:38:51,530 --> 00:38:52,200
Yes.

783
00:38:52,488 --> 00:38:53,666
Heibao taught him a lesson.

784
00:38:53,733 --> 00:38:54,330
That's great!

785
00:38:56,600 --> 00:38:57,680
That must've felt good, huh?

786
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:02,010
You've got guests?

787
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:02,890
No.

788
00:39:03,080 --> 00:39:04,560
Excuse me.

789
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:05,280
Coming!

790
00:39:12,010 --> 00:39:13,120
I found you.

791
00:39:13,240 --> 00:39:13,530
You...

792
00:39:14,010 --> 00:39:14,640
Le Shuishan...

793
00:39:14,711 --> 00:39:15,760
What are you doing here?

794
00:39:17,490 --> 00:39:17,970
Le Shuishan,

795
00:39:20,311 --> 00:39:22,760
