797
00:39:26,240 --> 00:39:28,490
You've really outdone
yourself, Le Shuishan.

798
00:39:33,050 --> 00:39:35,080
I'm here to give you a warning.

799
00:39:36,160 --> 00:39:38,760
If you dare smear my name again,

800
00:39:39,680 --> 00:39:41,560
