801
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:42,280
Get out!

802
00:39:42,311 --> 00:39:44,088
-You're not welcome here!
-Who are you?

803
00:39:44,155 --> 00:39:44,955
I... I'm...

804
00:39:45,850 --> 00:39:46,930
He's my boyfriend.

805
00:39:47,370 --> 00:39:47,970
My boyfriend!

806
00:39:48,600 --> 00:39:49,760
Not that tanned-skin guy?

807
00:39:51,533 --> 00:39:53,133
