a fair-skinned one now?

808
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,080
Le Shuishan,

809
00:39:55,640 --> 00:39:56,600
you're something else.

810
00:39:57,050 --> 00:39:59,720
Still good at making up stuff,

811
00:40:00,330 --> 00:40:03,680
but now you're even better
at switching men, huh?

812
00:40:03,810 --> 00:40:04,720
What nonsense is that?

813
00:40:04,970 --> 00:40:06,330
What? Am I wrong?

814
00:40:06,720 --> 00:40:09,120
You should be grateful
Zhang Yali died early!

815
00:40:10,160 --> 00:40:10,810
You know...

816
00:40:10,930 --> 00:40:11,410
Stop!

817
00:40:11,530 --> 00:40:12,050
Shut up!

818
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:14,120
- Get out!
- Shut up!

819
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:14,720
You old man!

820
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:15,970
Get out!

821
00:40:15,970 --> 00:40:17,450
What are you doing, old man?

822
00:40:17,890 --> 00:40:18,490
Out!

823
00:40:18,490 --> 00:40:20,450
Stop poking me!

824
00:40:20,640 --> 00:40:21,600
- Let it go!
- Go!

825
00:40:21,711 --> 00:40:23,760
Old man, you really want
to pick a fight with me?

826
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:24,160
You...

827
00:40:24,160 --> 00:40:24,560
Out!

828
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:26,810
Who are you?

829
00:40:26,810 --> 00:40:28,330
You're just one of her

830
00:40:29,850 --> 00:40:30,370
boyfriends.

831
00:40:31,711 --> 00:40:32,555
Tanned-skin man?

832
00:40:33,955 --> 00:40:34,720
Tanned-skin man...

833
00:40:39,200 --> 00:40:41,240
How dare you kick me!

834
00:40:41,370 --> 00:40:42,280
You listen to me,

835
00:40:42,560 --> 00:40:43,410
just you wait!

836
00:40:43,466 --> 00:40:44,490
I won't let this slide!

837
00:40:44,490 --> 00:40:45,370
This isn't over!

838
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:49,560
Don't touch me! Let go!

839
00:40:51,120 --> 00:40:52,050
This isn't over!

840
00:41:12,010 --> 00:41:12,970
How can someone

841
00:41:12,970 --> 00:41:14,410
be this awful?

842
00:41:16,890 --> 00:41:17,410
Shuishan,

843
00:41:18,080 --> 00:41:19,080
have some water.

844
00:41:23,680 --> 00:41:24,720
What do we do now?

845
00:41:25,644 --> 00:41:26,850
He's clearly not backing off.

846
00:41:27,422 --> 00:41:28,680
We can't just sit here scared.

847
00:41:28,733 --> 00:41:30,977
It's something from the past
that we have to solve.

848
00:41:31,530 --> 00:41:33,120
But now that he has

849
00:41:33,890 --> 00:41:34,850
even found your home.

850
00:41:35,600 --> 00:41:36,600
This is serious.

851
00:41:37,370 --> 00:41:38,370
